commit.message:
Improved user feedback

Users now lose the 'Block' button for an account that they've just
blocked.

Enhanced user feedback for blocking

You can't block people already on your block list; also fixed sticky
header.

Some front end and back end

Created modal, renamed file, imported twitter api functions into main
file

Basic website done

Created the page where you can add social media accounts, view your
block users, and search & block more users.
updated for fix with python 3.x & other fixes
rearranging things for flask and adding new page

Registration front-end added

Added form for registering for the website
blah.py has user authentication - not tested
